 and was eventually absorbed by the more successful French subsidiary, Waterman SA. Although this has now been absorbed in it's turn by Sanford, the writing instruments division of the huge American Newell corporation, Waterman remains based in France and the products retain a distinctive European look. Waterman pens are of exceptional quality and are highly recommended.</font></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1675760922517" class="gf_row gf_row-gap-15" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1675760922517" data-layout-lg="3+3+3+3" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="3+3+3+3" data-layout-sm="6+6+6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12+12+12" style="display: block; flex-wrap: unset; visibility: visible;" data-row-gap="15px"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-3 gf_col-md-3 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1675760922437" data-id="1675760922437" style="display: block; flex-direction: unset; justify-content: unset; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1680531480010" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1680531480010" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><a href="/products/waterman-man140-limited-edition-fountain-pen" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/06fbe07f-cdcd-4d25-b9d3-2ea8f908fc76/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/waterman-feature-tile-001.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" width="750" height="1000" natural-width="750" natural-height="1000" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></a></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-3 gf_col-md-3 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1675760947056" data-id="1675760947056" style="display: block; flex-direction: unset; justify-content: unset; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgrou